{"tid":1575488,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌曬你地 唔好再講「私了」 係自衛","createTime":"2019-09-17T01:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T04:29:09.000Z","uid":21010,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"826f9586ea41644175726d72705fc7b4550e1abd","tid":1575488,"uid":21010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:20:40.000Z","msg":"大家睇咗咁耐live 應該學咗咩叫最低武力<br />\n個頭流曬血都係好合理<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【人權小知識】自衛與法律風險<br />\n<br />\n面對襲擊或即時襲擊威脅時，如果出於必要自衛，是否違法？<br />\n<br />\n大家應保持克制，避免動武，並立即離開，避免受傷。若有必要，需自衛以保護自己免於即時危險，可屬合法抗辯，但必須是在該情況下使用合理武力，否則有可能構成普通襲擊或公眾地方打鬥罪等，惹上官非。自衛後亦要與對方保持距離，以免情況加劇。在場人士可盡量拍下情況，以便日後追究。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065609\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065609&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86raFdds9vdrezUgVRKRcn1wQ%3D&h=b2bf86a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065609&h=dbd0aa89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065609</a>"},{"pid":"0fd2ae75589d6771f4889bf00654a6267450a01f","tid":1575488,"uid":40276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:23:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3a11bf0ecdc43b31fce3a4ee0cf0f7bd53f5ffb","tid":1575488,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:31:55.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"3f598daab42d8802e3c0fca8cc09185a6adc0f85","tid":1575488,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:32:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3646bfcee9e4788e13da21fc7909d0783861a57e","tid":1575488,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:32:31.000Z","msg":"止暴制亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a741007315bd9a74da9aa1334bfe3be59156b452","tid":1575488,"uid":138934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:33